title: Spliced Business Formations Within Four Quarters: Total for All NAICS in Midwest Census Region
notes:
This series combines (splices) BFBF4QTOTALSAMW (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFBF4QTOTALSAMW) and BFPBF4QTOTALSAMW (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFPBF4QTOTALSAMW) to provide the entire time series for the actual and projected business formations within four quarters.

See the U.S. Census's FAQs (https://www.census.gov/econ/bfs/faqs.html) for more details.
